00:13:29.480 --> 00:13:31.139
Kaybettin.

00:13:31.140 --> 00:13:32.840
Ölümüne düş!

00:13:33.750 --> 00:13:37.710
O ikisi... sırada.

00:13:45.830 --> 00:13:46.880
Hey!

00:13:47.210 --> 00:13:48.300
Ingenium!

00:13:48.530 --> 00:13:51.019
